Hello guests and friends!  Our family is hosting Turo together. Tien Johnson, Lucky, and Kevin are our custodians taking care of the daily business. We became Turo host after so many trips of renting ourselves. We have traveled around the world to 76 countries. During our travels we received so much kindness from random strangers. We became kinder after each journey.  

One time, we walked by a beach park and saw a group of Egyptians in Alexandria grilling fish and bbq lamb. The smell was irresistible. We decided to walk back and forth until they invited us in. No shame, hehehe. And of course, that one time in a small suburb near Dijon in France, we had no GPS and could not find our Airbnb. We made a wrong turn into the private property of an old French famer. Between my husband and I, we could cover lots of languages but French; maybe not so much. The couple did not seem to understand there was a hotel in their town but recognized the last name when we showed them the address. They then jumped into their car and signaled us to follow them. After they guided us to the correct place, I said merci and tears came down so happy watching their car drove away into sunset on the mountain range. And believe it or not, we invited a random guest to have thanksgiving with us because he was alone in town during the holiday. That’s how we are and how we want our world to be.   

We have learned so much from hosting Turo. One guest gave us “Second City” tickets; others left chocolate. Those we kept. But we reached out to one guest who left a $3000 drone. We shipped it right back to him. We love to hear your stories about your first time in Chicago or coming back home to the Windy City for a visit. Please feel free to reach out. Facebook https://www.facebook.com/tien.t.chau

At Revv Motors, we believe that every journey tells a story, and we are dedicated to making each one memorable and enjoyable for our hosts and guests. Our commitment to excellence, safety, and customer satisfaction drives everything we do.

**About Revv Motors:**
Revv Motors is a trusted and reliable name in the automotive rental industry. Our team comprises passionate travel enthusiasts who understand the importance of a seamless travel experience. We take pride in providing top-notch vehicles that ensure comfort, safety, and style for every trip, whether it's a quick business commute or a long-awaited vacation.

**Our Commitment:**
We are committed to maintaining the highest standards of service and quality. Our vehicles are meticulously maintained and regularly inspected to ensure they are in perfect condition for every journey. We understand the importance of reliability and safety on the road, and we strive to provide our customers with peace of mind every time they choose Revv Motors.

**Travel Experiences:**
Our team has a wealth of travel experience, and we bring that expertise to every interaction with our customers. From exploring the scenic routes of the Pacific Coast Highway to navigating the bustling streets of New York City, we know what it takes to make a trip special. Our goal is to share our love for travel and help our customers create their own unforgettable memories.

**Our Vehicle:**
At Revv Motors, we currently offer a meticulously maintained vehicle that caters to a variety of travel needs. Equipped with the latest features and amenities, our vehicle ensures a comfortable and enjoyable ride for every traveler.

**Connect with Us:**
We value the relationships we build with our hosts and guests. Stay connected with us and keep up with the latest news, updates, and travel tips by following us on all social platforms at Revv Motorsports. We love hearing from our community and sharing the joys of travel together.

Thank you for choosing Revv Motors. We look forward to being a part of your next adventure and helping you create memories that will last a lifetime.

Safe travels!

The Revv Motors Team
